	[sam.sleep
		|Just as you’re crawling into bed, the door to your quarters opens, and Sam scurries in[sam.pregStage 1
			| cradling her gravid belly,
		] wearing an oversized t-shirt and a pair of boxer shorts.[sam.pregStage 1
