		] With surprising speed she climbs into bed to your left, pulling the sheets up to her chin right away before rolling onto her own left side. Even after all the bonding you’ve done with her, it seems she still can’t totally overcome her shyness.

		<i>“[pc.name]?”</i> Sam mutters, looking back over her shoulder with a blush. Her tone is expectant, but she’s clearly embarrassed even though this isn’t your first time sleeping together.

		You know exactly what she wants, so you spare her having to ask you directly for it. You rub her arm tenderly and kiss her neck before sliding over and spooning her, slipping one arm under her and another over her. Sam grasps your right hand with hers, guiding your arm to wrap around her[sam.pregStage 1
