			| though she squeaks at first,
		] she soon melts into your arms, her tail wagging as much as it can between your bodies.

		Just like always, the intimacy is undeniable: holding your lover so close, feeling her heart beating, breathing her unique scent[sam.pregStage 1
			|, feeling the pup[sam.currentPupsRange 2
